Review:
Experience the union of south asian flavours at NONYA ✨
the only Pan Asian restaurant in Ahmedabad. Who represents almost every region of South Asia. Nonya at Taj skyline. They are serving veg as well as non-veg authentic Asian taste from the parts of south Asian countries. But with INDIAN taste.
